ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢幾好丫<br />\n<br />\n份人唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 見過佢 官黎講佢唔算好離地 都大概知平民午餐咩價位 雖然同我地講三十幾四十蚊午餐黎講已經算平 上年既事"},{"pid":"18f4e5b3195b646c429521f778b016c3d6a7cc98","tid":88859,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢幾好丫<br />\n<br />\n份人唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 見過佢 官黎講佢唔算好離地 都大概知平民午餐咩價位 雖然同我地講三十幾四十蚊午餐黎講已經算平 上年既事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢做勞工處處長時我做緊勞工處<br />\n每日要返18小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢完全無諗過要請人"}]}